    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es tohpu ta patt lihdsi-\nnahts/ ka kas Dsittuma no-\ngrimst/ es efinu ka Wihrs/ kam\nSpehka newaid.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es efinu teem Nomirru-\nscheem peeschkirts/ itt ka tee No-\nkanti/ kas Rappâ gull/ ko tu\nwairs ne peeminnt/ un kas no\ntawas Rohkas atschkirti irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu ehi mannis dsittara Bedre lizzis/ eeksch Tuuntibas\nun Dsittumeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tawa Bahrsiba manni speesch/ tu apbehdini mann ar\nwisfeem taweem Pluhdeem/\nSela.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Mannus Pasihstamus efi\ntu tahfu no mannim lizzis/ tu\nehi mann teem par leelu Negan-\ntibu darrijs/ es efinu apsflehgts/\nun ne warnu istikt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Manna Azs behdajahs\nto Behdu deht/ ak KUNGS!\nes peesanuzu tewis zaur wisfu\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Woj tu tad starp te\nNomirruscheem Brihnumus d\nriti? jeb zeltees tee Preekscha-\nun tewi pateiks? Sela.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Arrig tawa Schehlast-\ntaps Rappa fluddinata/ un wa Peetizziba eektch Samai\nschanas?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Arrig tawi Brihnu\nTumfiba taps pasibti? un tai\nTaifniba tai Semmiê/ kur\nneeka tohp peenuinnehts?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet es peesanuzu teivi\nKIINGSS/ un manna Luhgfch\nna nahk agri preeksch tewis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kapehz atstum tu KUNG\nmannu Dwehseli/ un paslep tu Waigu no mannim?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Es efinu behdigs un n\nwahrdsis no patt Jaunibas/\npaneftu tawas Istruhzinasch\nnas/ ka es gann drihs isfanistu\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tawas Bahrsibas pa-\nmannim eet/ tawas Istruhzina\nschanas nospatda manni.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tee mettahs aptahr\nmann ka Uhdens zaur augosch\nDeenu/tee apstabjahs kahrt man\nnim kohpa.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tu darri/ ka Draugi tu\nTuwaki tahtu no mannim pa\nleek/ manni Pasihstamee preek-\nmannim apsflepjahs.\n"
